{subhead}FreeSpace:The Great War Game Released{def}
{left}
{pp}
The latest space war simulation, Freespace, has now been released by
Hyperion on the Amiga. You play a pilot in the war of the Terrans verses
the Vasudans. Over 30 missions consist of search and destroy espionage missions
and some epic battles.
{pp}
Requires a 060 or PPC based Amiga with Graphics card, 3D accelerator, 64Mb RAM
and 8x CDROM. A demo is available.
{pp}
{link http://www.amigaflame.demon.co.uk/}http://www.amigaflame.demon.co.uk/{end}
{pp}